# Project Run Commands

## Linting
Run lint using the following command:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:eslint --fix
```
Example: `npx nx run seller_ai_model_pegasus:eslint --fix`

For Perseus applications like order_page_perseus, you can also run stylelint:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:stylelint
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:stylelint`

## Testing
Run tests using the following command:
```bash
npx nx test <PROJECT>
```
Example: `npx nx test seller_ai_model_pegasus`

Run specific tests using the following command:
```bash
nx test <PROJECT> <TEST_FILE_PATH>
```
Example: `nx test seller_ai_model_pegasus apps/seller_ai_model_pegasus/specs/announcements/announcements.e2e.spec.ts`

For Perseus applications, run end-to-end tests:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:e2e
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:e2e`

## Running Applications
Run a Perseus application:
```bash
npx nx start <PROJECT>
```
Example: `npx nx start order_page_perseus`

Run just the server component:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:server
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:server`

## Building Applications
Build a project:
```bash
npx nx build <PROJECT>
```
Example: `npx nx build order_page_perseus`

For Perseus applications, compile the server:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:compile
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:compile`

## Storybook
Run Storybook:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:storybook
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:storybook`

Build Storybook:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:build-storybook
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:build-storybook`

## Translation
Generate translations:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:translate
```
Example: `npx nx run order_page_perseus:translate`

## Pre-Push Preparation
Run pre-push preparation using the following command:
```bash
npx nx run <PROJECT>:test-coverage && npx nx run <PROJECT>:eslint --fix && npx nx format:write
```
Example: `npx nx run seller_ai_model_pegasus:test-coverage && npx nx run seller_ai_model_pegasus:eslint --fix && npx nx format:write`

For Perseus applications:
```bash
npx nx test <PROJECT> && npx nx run <PROJECT>:eslint --fix && npx nx run <PROJECT>:stylelint && npx nx format:write
```
Example: `npx nx test order_page_perseus && npx nx run order_page_perseus:eslint --fix && npx nx run order_page_perseus:stylelint && npx nx format:write`
